            <category>
                <![CDATA[Watch S4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303865</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>除了两款新耳机外，小米近日亦发布了最新款的智能手表 Watch S4，Edward 亦同样试用了一段时间，现在就与大家分享一下使用体验吧。</p><h2>小米 Watch S4 开箱直击</h2><p>同样地，为大家分享小米 Watch S4 这款全新智能手表的使用体验前，先让 Edward 为大家带来它的开箱直击吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305161" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01931-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01931-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01931.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是小米最新推出的智能手表 Watch S4 的包装盒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305162" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01933-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01933-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01933.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲从包装已可看到，小米 Watch S4 支援蓝牙 5.3 制式，是可以配对 iPhone 或 Android 手机使用的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01941-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01941-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01941.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一打开包装盒，就见到 Watch S4 的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305164" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01944-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01944-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01944.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而底层就放了说明书及 Watch S4 专属的磁吸式 USB 充电线，开箱部分至此结束。</p><h2>设计平实走大众路线</h2><p>今次小米推出的 Watch S4 智能手表，设有黑、银及特别的黑彩虹色设计，不过设计上无论哪种颜色，Watch S4 都是走偏向沉实风的大众路线，不过话虽如此，但外观看起来 Watch S4 还是十分不错，很有一般传统腕表的感觉。另外 Watch S4 亦有不少不同质地的表带供用家选购，除了附送的氟橡胶表带，亦有尼龙或小牛皮物料选择，颜色亦有橙、蓝、白等，用来配衬服装十分不错。除了表带外，Watch S4 亦可替换表圈，而购买表带时包装内亦有对应相同风格的表圈附送，用家可以与不同表带作一套风格装上，或者可以自行 mix and match，同样十分不错，当中灰蓝色双时区的表带及表圈设计，以灰、蓝双色各半以展示不同时区最为特别，设计亦最抢眼，亦是笔者个人最爱。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305166" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01973-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01973-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01973.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Watch S4 表身采用了金属物料制造，感觉颇为硬净，而笔者测试的是黑色表身，设计风格较为平实。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305167" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01968-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01968-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01968.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲表冠颇为漂亮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305168" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01970-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01970-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01970.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而下方就设有功能键。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305169" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01983-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01983-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01983.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305170" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01985-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01985-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01985.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而 Watch S4 最特别的设计，就是连表圈都可以替换。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305171" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01987-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01987-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01987.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲基本上只要将表圈内侧的橙色实心标志，与表盘上的橙色外框标志对准再扭动表圈，就可以将它装上表上。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305172" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01958-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01958-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01958.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305173" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01956-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01956-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01956.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于表带方面，黑色版本附送的是氟橡胶表带，虽然是塑胶但感觉物料颇为亲肤。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01964-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01964-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01964.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而表带同样是可以替换的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01992-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01992-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01992.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲表盘的设计亦与传统手表十分相似。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_202504171-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_202504171-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_202504171.jpg 405w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当然，预设亦有不同设计的表面供用家选用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01999-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01999-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01999.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02001.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲部分表面更可让用家自行设定显示内容。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01993-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01993-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01993.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01994-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01994-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01994.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而按实荧幕就可以在不同表面之间切换使用。</p><br /><b>
]]>
